    {
      "type": "p",
      "content": "Sophisticated composition demands more than line breaks: justified text must expand inter-word space with precision, hyphenation must honour syllable structure, bidirectional passages must alternate direction without visual artefacts, and every decision must be deterministic regardless of platform or run order."
